		   <ThingDef ParentName="GE_Hat">
    <defName>GE_Hat_cowl</defName>
    <label>Citizen hood</label>
    <description>A mostly unassuming hood in a kemetic style, with a visor made of solid gold. The visor was originally completely solid to represent humanity being helpless without the guidance of the gods. However, when that was tested in a ritual, one person fell into a lit brazier and three people fell into large jugs of wine. The visor now has eye slits to allow unhindered sight.</description>
	
	 <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/Apparel/Hats/B/CowlG</texPath>
